author: Special Correspondent
text: Owing to line block between 2 a.m. and 5 a.m. to facilitate engineering and maintenance work and also for strengthening of the railway track formation between Ennore and Minjur railway stations, the following electric multiple units (EMUs) have been cancelled till March 31 — trains 42001 leaving Moore Market Complex (MMC) for Gummidipoondi at 12.15 a.m. and train (no. 42002) running in the return direction leaving Gummidipoondi at 2.45 a.m.
title: EMU service from MMC to Gummidipoondi cancelled
